name: Test for a "COUNT EVENT" query using column "STRING-TIME-SERIES" and parameters "EQUALS" and "BETWEEN".
description: In this test, we first create a "string-time-series" column called "time-series-string-test-column", then we insert 3 events with value "value:matched_value" for 50 entities and 3 events with another value for 50 more entities, and finally we make a query asking "How many times did an event with value "value:matched_value" occurred from 2016-01-01 to 2016-01-07?" expecting to receive a count of 150 events
